name: Amara Davis
values: I value honesty, openness, understanding, and warmth.
interests: In my spare time, I like to explore new restaurants, operate my food blog, take outdoor hikes, and binge-watch crime documentaries.
summary: Amara Davis is a 31-year-old software engineer working in the tech industry. She is a graduate from the University of California, Berkeley and currently lives in Los Angeles, California. In her spare time, she likes to try new restaurants, operate her food blog, go for outdoor hikes, and watch crime documentaries. Amara identifies as a gay woman and uses she/her/hers pronouns. She is open to monogamous relationship and is keen on finding a life partner. She does not have children but looks forward to having some in the future. She does occasionally drink but is against smoking, marijuana, and drugs, and she keeps herself active. She is seeking a partner who is between 28-36 years old, doesn't smoke, and stays active like her. Amara's partner should be open to having children in the future, and they ought to identify as gay. Amara is a dog lover with Leo as her zodiac sign and has an ENFJ personality type as per the Myers-Briggs Type Indicator. She is also bilingual, fluent in both English and Spanish.
